图片来源：图虫“ 声明称，经查证，石正丽研究员从未发布过任何相关信息，石正丽本人及该所保留追究造谣者法律责任的权利。
Source: Toothworm statement said Shi Zhengli researchers have never released any relevant information, and Shi Zhengli and the institute reserve the right to prosecute the perpetrators of disinformation.
”针对网络流传的石正丽称蚊虫或成新冠病毒第三宿主相关消息，2020年3月17日，中国科学院武汉病毒研究所发布声明予以辟谣。
A statement released March 17, 2020 by the Wuhan Institute of Virus of the Chinese Academy of Sciences denied rumours that Shizheng Li, a cyber-circulating mosquito, had become the third host of the new crown virus.
武汉病毒研究所在官网发布声明称，近期网络流传题为《石正丽凌晨发出警告：对疫情不必抱有太大乐观，蚊虫或成第三宿主》的不实信息，该谣言可能造成恶劣的社会影响。
According to a recent online bulletin published on the website, Shi Zhengli warned that there was no need to be too optimistic about the outbreak, mosquitoes or third hosts, a myth that could have dire social consequences.
此前有自媒体引述知情人士透露的消息称，3月16日凌晨，石正丽对世界疫情作了全面分析，石正丽称目前中国和世界的疫情形势仍然严峻，夏日即将到来时更加不能能掉以轻心，她认为对4月底结束全球病情不必抱有太大乐观，蚊虫将会成为冠状病毒的新型传播方式。
In the early morning hours of March 16, Shi Zhengli made a comprehensive analysis of the situation in China and the world, saying the situation in China and the world was still dire and summer could not be taken lightly, according to a source quoted in the media as saying.
武汉病毒所声明称，经查证，石正丽研究员从未发布过任何相关信息，石正丽本人及该所保留追究造谣者法律责任的权利。
Wuhan virus declared that, after verification, Shi Zhengli researcher has never issued any relevant information, Shi Zhengli and the Institute reserve the right to pursue the perpetrators of the rumor legal responsibility.
据官网资料显示，石正丽系武汉病毒研究所新发传染病研究中心主任、生物安全工作委员会主任、新发病毒学科组组长。
According to the official website, Shi Zhengli is the director of Wuhan Institute of Virus Research Center for Emerging Infectious Diseases, director of the biosafety working committee, and head of the new virus science team.
石正丽被外界誉为“蝙蝠女侠”，因其在SARS病毒溯源的研究中证实了蝙蝠是SARS冠状病毒的自然宿主。
Shi Zhengli has been hailed as the "Bat Woman" because her research into the origin of the SARS virus has confirmed that bats are the natural hosts of the SARS coronavirus.
新冠肺炎疫情爆发后，武汉病毒研究所成为舆论关注焦点。
After the outbreak of new crown pneumonia, Wuhan virus research institute became the focus of public opinion.
石正丽早前曾专门辟谣“病毒是从P4泄露”相关传言，此后在2月15日，网络曾流传“武汉病毒研究所一名女研究生黄某某是新冠病毒肺炎零号病人”的消息，2月16日“武汉病毒研究所研究员陈某某实名举报武汉病毒研究所所长泄露病毒”的消息又受到关注。
After earlier rumors that the virus was leaking from the P4, Shi Zhengli on Feb. 15 reported that a female graduate student at Wuhan Virus Research Institute, Huang Mou-mou, was reported to be the No.
据官网资料，中国科学院武汉病毒研究所成立于1956年，是专业从事病毒学基础研究及相关技术创新的综合性研究机构。
According to the website, Wuhan Institute of Virus of the Chinese Academy of Sciences was founded in 1956 and is specialized in basic virology research and related technological innovation.
现有在职职工268人，拥有在学研究生325人。
There are 268 active employees and 325 graduate students.
针对外界争议，武汉病毒研究所曾于2月19日在官网发布《致全所职工和研究生的一封信》。
In response to external controversy, Wuhan Institute of Virus Research on February 19 in the official website published a "letter to the entire staff and graduate students."
公开信称，近期网络流传涉及该所若干谣言，对该所科研人员造成极大伤害，严重干扰了应急科研攻关任务。
The open letter said that the recent spread of a number of rumors involving the Institute, the Institute's researchers caused great harm, seriously interfered with the task of emergency scientific research.
这些谣言“对坚守科研一线的我所科研人员造成极大的伤害，也严重干扰了我所承担的战‘疫’应急科研攻关任务。
These rumors "to adhere to the line of scientific research caused great harm to my research staff, but also seriously interfered with my 'epidemic' emergency scientific research mission.
回首过去一个多月的艰辛付出，我们问心无愧。
Looking back on the past more than a month of hard work, we clear conscience.
”公开信表示。
"said the letter.
